## Limitations
This report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023. Some sources may have been published after this date, and the information may not fully capture the most recent trends or data. Additionally, the findings are based on secondary sources, which may not provide the depth of insight that primary research could offer. The perspectives included are primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent global trends in healthcare worker resignations.